<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/tasks/br-00057-brazilian-taxes-sales-quotation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">On the Action Pane, click Follow up.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/tasks/br-00057-brazilian-taxes-sales-quotation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">Click Confirm.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/tasks/br-00057-brazilian-taxes-sales-quotation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">Click Yes.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/tasks/br-00057-brazilian-taxes-sales-quotation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">In the Reason field, enter or select a value.</li>
